.title Developer Services

These services provide a vast array of tools for the professional 
developer.  Through an active relationship with companies such as
Intel and SunSoft, SCO provides a wide variety of the latest
programming tools and development environments, including C, C++,
and Java code.

Developer Services: 

  UnixWare & SCO OpenServer   - C and C++ development tools
  Development Kit 7

  SCO Java Development Kit    - Java development tools

  SCO Edition of Sun's        - Integrated Java development
  Java Workshop                 environment
 
Visit the SCO web site at www.sco.com for more information.
